RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT A.STATUS, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES B WHERE A.STATUS =B.STATUS_CODE AND B.STATUS_TYPE = 'C' AND A.PRODUCT = NVL(?, A.PRODUCT)ORDER BY A.STATUS
SELECT DISTINCT A.STATUS, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES B WHERE A.STATUS =B.STATUS_CODE AND B.STATUS_TYPE = 'C' ORDER BY A.STATUS

SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO,USER_REF_NO,PRODUCT,COUNTERPARTY,AUTH_STATUS,CONTRACT_STATUS,CURRENCY,AMOUNT_FINANCED,CONT_AMOUNT,PRINCIPAL_OUTSTANDING_BAL FROM OLVW_CONTRACT_SUMMARY WHERE module_code = 'OL' AND CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A','L') AND BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND USER_DEFINED_STATUS = ? AND PRODUCT = NVL(?,PRODUCT) AND AUTH_STATUS='A' ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION, RTGS_PRODUCT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR B, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD C WHERE A.MODULE = 'OL' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND B.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT K, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = K.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE) ORDER BY A.PRODUCT_CODE
